<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Hire Right Solution</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Executive Search, Background Check, and Payroll Outsourcing in Vietnam."
    />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #ffffff;
        --text: #1f2937;
        --heading: #172554;
        --muted: #64748b;
        --line: #e5e7eb;
        --blue: #1e3a8a;
        --blue-strong: #2563eb;
        --blue-soft: #dbeafe;
        --sky: #7dd3fc;
        --slate-950: #020617;
        --slate-900: #0f172a;
        --slate-800: #1e293b;
        --slate-700: #334155;
        --slate-300: #cbd5e1;
        --slate-200: #e2e8f0;
        --white-08: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        --white-10: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        --shadow-lg: 0 20px 60px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
        --shadow-xl: 0 24px 60px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.18);
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      html {
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        min-width: 320px;
        font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
        color: var(--text);
        background: var(--bg);
      }

      a {
        color: inherit;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      button,
      input,
      select,
      textarea {
        font: inherit;
      }

      button {
        border: 0;
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      img {
        max-width: 100%;
        display: block;
      }

      .container {
        width: min(100% - 32px, 1280px);
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .section {
        padding: 96px 0;
      }

      .eyebrow {
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.28em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .section-title {
        margin: 20px 0 0;
        font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
        line-height: 1.05;
        letter-spacing: -0.04em;
        font-weight: 800;
      }

      .section-copy {
        margin-top: 24px;
        font-size: 1.125rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
      }

      .site-nav {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        z-index: 50;
        width: 100%;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
        backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
      }

      .site-nav .container {
        display: flex;
        height: 80px;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
      }

      .brand {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 16px;
      }

      .brand-mark {
        display: inline-flex;
        height: 56px;
        width: 56px;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        border-radius: 14px;
        background: #31469a;
        color: #fff;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(49, 70, 154, 0.22);
      }

      .brand-mark svg {
        width: 28px;
        height: 28px;
      }

      .brand-name {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
        color: #25356f;
      }

      .desktop-nav {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 42px;
      }

      .desktop-nav a {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #4b5563;
      }

      .desktop-nav a:hover {
        color: var(--blue);
      }

      .btn-primary {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 12px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: #31469a;
        padding: 16px 32px;
        color: #fff;
        font-weight: 700;
        box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(49, 70, 154, 0.28);
        transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease;
      }

      .btn-primary:hover {
        transform: translateY(-1px);
        background: #3b53b5;
        box-shadow: 0 22px 48px rgba(49, 70, 154, 0.34);
      }

      .btn-secondary {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        color: #dbeafe;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .btn-outline {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        border: 2px solid #1e40af;
        border-radius: 14px;
        padding: 16px 20px;
        background: #fff;
        color: #1e40af;
        font-size: 1.125rem;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .btn-outline:hover {
        background: #eff6ff;
      }

      .mobile-toggle {
        display: none;
        background: transparent;
        color: #4b5563;
        font-size: 1.75rem;
        line-height: 1;
      }

      .mobile-panel {
        display: none;
        border-top: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
        background: #fff;
        padding: 8px 16px 16px;
      }

      .mobile-panel.open {
        display: block;
      }

      .mobile-panel a,
      .mobile-panel button {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 12px 14px;
        background: transparent;
        text-align: left;
        color: #374151;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .mobile-panel a:hover,
      .mobile-panel button:hover {
        background: #eff6ff;
        color: var(--blue);
      }

      .hero {
        position: relative;
        display: flex;
        min-height: 100vh;
        align-items: center;
        overflow: hidden;
        padding-top: 80px;
        background-color: #020617; /* Thêm nền tối dự phòng */
        color: #fff;
      }

      .hero-bg,
      .hero-bg::before,
      .hero-bg::after {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        right: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
      }

      .hero-bg {
        background-image:
          linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(91, 115, 196, 0.38) 0%, rgba(8, 13, 27, 0.66) 54%, rgba(6, 10, 20, 0.92) 100%),
          radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(122, 152, 255, 0.24), transparent 36%),
          linear-gradient(rgba(11, 18, 38, 0.82), rgba(11, 18, 38, 0.82)),
          url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1486406146926-c627a92ad1ab?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop");
        background-position: center;
        background-size: cover;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
      }

      .hero-content {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        width: 100%;
        padding: 96px 0;
      }

      .hero-title {
        max-width: 1080px;
        margin: 0;
        font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 8vw, 7rem);
        line-height: 0.95;
        letter-spacing: -0.06em;
        font-weight: 900;
      }

      .hero-copy {
        max-width: 980px;
        margin-top: 32px;
        font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 2.2vw, 2rem);
        line-height: 1.55;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
      }

      .hero-actions {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 20px;
        align-items: center;
        margin-top: 44px;
      }

      .hero-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 16px;
        max-width: 1020px;
        margin-top: 48px;
      }

      .glass-card {
        border: 1px solid var(--white-10);
        border-radius: 24px;
        background: var(--white-08);
        padding: 20px;
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      }

      .glass-card .icon {
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        color: #bfdbfe;
        font-size: 1.4rem;
      }

      .glass-card h3 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.18em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #dbeafe;
      }

      .glass-card p {
        margin: 12px 0 0;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        line-height: 1.75;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
      }

      .dark-section {
        background: var(--slate-950);
        color: #fff;
      }

      .two-col {
        display: grid;
        gap: 32px;
        align-items: start;
      }

      .proof-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 1.4fr;
      }

      .proof-cards,
      .validation-cards,
      .faq-grid,
      .why-grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 20px;
      }

      .proof-cards {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }

      .dark-card {
        border: 1px solid var(--white-10);
        border-radius: 28px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
        padding: 24px;
      }

      .dark-card h3,
      .service-card h3,
      .faq-card h3,
      .why-card h3,
      .package-card h3 {
        margin: 0;
      }

      .dark-card p,
      .service-card p,
      .faq-card p,
      .why-card p,
      .package-card p {
        margin: 12px 0 0;
      }

      .light-center {
        max-width: 860px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .services-wrap {
        display: grid;
        gap: 32px;
        margin-top: 64px;
      }

      .service-card {
        display: grid;
        gap: 32px;
        grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
        border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        border-radius: 32px;
        background: #f8fafc;
        padding: 40px;
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
      }

      .service-card.inverse {
        border-color: #0f172a;
        background: #020617;
        color: #fff;
      }

      .service-badge {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        border-radius: 999px;
        padding: 10px 16px;
        font-size: 0.76rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: 0.24em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .service-card:not(.inverse) .service-badge {
        background: #dbeafe;
        color: #1d4ed8;
      }

      .service-card.inverse .service-badge {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        color: #7dd3fc;
      }

      .service-card h3 {
        margin-top: 24px;
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 3rem);
        line-height: 1.1;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      }

      .service-card .copy {
        font-size: 1.125rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: #475569;
      }

      .service-card.inverse .copy,
      .service-card.inverse .bullet-list span {
        color: #cbd5e1;
      }

      .service-side {
        border-radius: 28px;
        background: #fff;
        padding: 28px;
      }

      .service-card.inverse .service-side {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      }

      .service-side .mini-icon,
      .why-card .mini-icon {
        display: inline-flex;
        height: 56px;
        width: 56px;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        border-radius: 18px;
        font-size: 1.35rem;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .service-card:not(.inverse) .mini-icon {
        background: #eff6ff;
        color: #1d4ed8;
      }

      .service-card.inverse .mini-icon,
      .why-card .mini-icon {
        background: rgba(125, 211, 252, 0.12);
        color: #7dd3fc;
      }

      .service-side h4 {
        margin: 24px 0 0;
        font-size: 1.125rem;
      }

      .bullet-list {
        margin: 20px 0 0;
        padding: 0;
        list-style: none;
      }

      .bullet-list li {
        display: flex;
        gap: 12px;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      .bullet-list li + li {
        margin-top: 16px;
      }

      .check {
        color: #10b981;
        font-weight: 800;
      }

      .service-card.inverse .check {
        color: #7dd3fc;
      }

      .validation-section {
        background: #f8fafc;
      }

      .validation-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 0.95fr 1.05fr;
      }

      .validation-callout {
        margin-top: 32px;
        border: 1px solid #dbeafe;
        border-radius: 24px;
        background: #eff6ff;
        padding: 24px;
        color: #172554;
      }

      .validation-cards .card,
      .faq-card {
        border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        border-radius: 28px;
        background: #fff;
        padding: 28px;
        box-shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
      }

      .packages-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 32px;
      }

      .package-card {
        position: relative;
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: 32px;
      }

      .package-card.standard {
        border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        background: rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.7);
        box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
      }

      .package-card.featured {
        border: 2px solid #3b82f6;
        background: #fff;
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
        transform: translateY(-20px);
      }

      .popular-pill {
        position: absolute;
        left: 50%;
        top: 0;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: #3b82f6;
        padding: 8px 20px;
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .package-kicker {
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.2em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #2563eb;
      }

      .package-card h3 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: -0.04em;
        color: #0f172a;
      }

      .package-summary {
        min-height: 64px;
        color: #64748b;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      .package-tier {
        margin: 24px 0 32px;
        font-size: 3.5rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: -0.05em;
        color: #0f172a;
      }

      .why-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }

      .why-card {
        border: 1px solid var(--white-10);
        border-radius: 28px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
        padding: 24px;
      }

      .faq-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }

      .footer {
        border-top: 1px solid #1e293b;
        background: #020617;
        padding: 80px 0 40px;
        color: #cbd5e1;
      }

      .footer-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.8fr 0.8fr 0.9fr;
        gap: 48px;
      }

      .footer h2,
      .footer h3 {
        color: #fff;
      }

      .footer p,
      .footer li,
      .footer a {
        line-height: 1.8;
      }

      .footer-list {
        margin: 24px 0 0;
        padding: 0;
        list-style: none;
      }

      .footer-list li + li {
        margin-top: 12px;
      }

      .footer-bottom {
        margin-top: 56px;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        padding-top: 24px;
        color: #64748b;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }

      .modal {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        right: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 0;
        z-index: 80;
        display: none;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 24px;
        background: rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.68);
        backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      }

      .modal.open {
        display: flex;
      }

      .modal-card {
        width: min(100%, 640px);
        border-radius: 28px;
        background: #fff;
        padding: 32px;
        box-shadow: 0 28px 80px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.22);
      }

      .modal-close {
        float: right;
        background: transparent;
        color: #64748b;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }

      .form-grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 16px;
        margin-top: 24px;
      }

      .field label {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #1e293b;
      }

      .input-light {
        width: 100%;
        border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 12px 16px;
        outline: none;
      }

      .input-light:focus {
        border-color: #3b82f6;
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.18);
      }

      .submit-note {
        margin-top: 8px;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
        color: #6b7280;
      }

      .success-box {
        display: none;
        padding: 16px 0 8px;
      }

      .success-box.open {
        display: block;
      }

      .success-icon {
        display: inline-flex;
        height: 56px;
        width: 56px;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: #dbeafe;
        color: #1d4ed8;
        font-size: 1.75rem;
      }

      .arrow {
        font-size: 1.1em;
      }

      @media (max-width: 1100px) {
        .hero-grid,
        .packages-grid,
        .footer-grid,
        .proof-cards,
        .faq-grid,
        .why-grid {
          grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
        }

        .proof-grid,
        .validation-grid,
        .service-card {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .package-card.featured {
          transform: none;
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 860px) {
        .desktop-nav {
          display: none;
        }

        .mobile-toggle {
          display: inline-flex;
        }

        .hero-content {
          padding: 72px 0;
        }

        .hero-grid,
        .proof-cards,
        .packages-grid,
        .why-grid,
        .faq-grid,
        .footer-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .section {
          padding: 80px 0;
        }

        .service-card,
        .modal-card {
          padding: 24px;
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 640px) {
        .container {
          width: min(100% - 24px, 1280px);
        }

        .brand-name {
          font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .brand-mark {
          height: 48px;
          width: 48px;
        }

        .hero-title {
          font-size: 3.4rem;
        }

        .hero-copy {
          font-size: 1.15rem;
        }

        .btn-primary,
        .btn-outline {
          width: 100%;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <nav class="site-nav">
      <div class="container">
        <a href="#top" class="brand">
          <span class="brand-mark" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M12 3l7 3v6c0 4.6-3 8.9-7 10-4-1.1-7-5.4-7-10V6l7-3z"></path>
              <path d="M9.2 11.8l1.9 1.9 3.7-4.2"></path>
            </svg>
          </span>
          <span class="brand-name">Hire Right Solution</span>
        </a>

        <div class="desktop-nav">
          <a href="#services">Services</a>
          <a href="#proof">Proof</a>
          <a href="#packages">Packages</a>
          <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
          <button class="btn-primary" data-open-modal>Schedule a Consultation</button>
        </div>

        <button class="mobile-toggle" id="mobileToggle" aria-label="Toggle navigation">☰</button>
      </div>

      <div class="mobile-panel" id="mobilePanel">
        <a href="#services">Services</a>
        <a href="#proof">Proof</a>
        <a href="#packages">Packages</a>
        <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
        <button data-open-modal>Schedule a Consultation</button>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <main id="top">
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-bg"></div>
        <div class="hero-content">
          <div class="container">
            <p class="eyebrow" style="color:#bfdbfe; margin:0 0 24px;">Hire Right Solution</p>
            <h1 class="hero-title">
              Executive Search, Background Check, and Payroll Outsourcing in Vietnam.
            </h1>
            <p class="hero-copy">
              Hire Right Solution helps employers enter, hire, screen, and operate in Vietnam with
              background verification workflows, confidential executive search support, and payroll
              outsourcing coordination designed for local execution.
            </p>
            <div class="hero-actions">
              <button class="btn-primary" data-open-modal>
                Schedule a Consultation <span class="arrow">→</span>
              </button>
              <a class="btn-secondary" href="#services">Explore Core Services <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
            </div>

            <div class="hero-grid">
              <article class="glass-card">
                <div class="icon">🌐</div>
                <h3>Vietnam-Focused</h3>
                <p>Background screening, executive search, and payroll support built for local hiring and operating realities.</p>
              </article>
              <article class="glass-card">
                <div class="icon">🛡️</div>
                <h3>Employer-Grade</h3>
                <p>Structured workflows designed for hiring teams, finance leads, and regional operators who need dependable execution.</p>
              </article>
              <article class="glass-card">
                <div class="icon">🔒</div>
                <h3>Confidential Delivery</h3>
                <p>Suitable for sensitive leadership searches, candidate screening, and internal stakeholder coordination.</p>
              </article>
              <article class="glass-card">
                <div class="icon">👥</div>
                <h3>Consultative Support</h3>
                <p>Strategic guidance for employers entering Vietnam or tightening risk controls around local operations.</p>
              </article>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="proof" class="section dark-section">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="two-col proof-grid">
            <div>
              <p class="eyebrow" style="color:#7dd3fc; margin:0;">Proof and Positioning</p>
